B.6.20 postaction
-----------------

*postaction [_option_...] install [shortcut|fileassoc|script] [_pkg_...]*

*postaction [_option_...] remove [shortcut|fileassoc|script] [_pkg_...]*

     Carry out the postaction 'shortcut', 'fileassoc', or 'script' given
